Serpentors eye beams forced Lunarpines paw away, more pain shot through his
body. he knew what would happen if he were to let go so he kept hold of
Serpentors arm trying to rip it off. His paw hit the ground and caused a
sudden wave through his body. repairs were continueing but the alliance bot
was causing damage as the other damage was being repaired. Despite the pain
the wolf slashed again, this time at Serpentors eyes, disable the snakes
optics and the fight would be as good as won.

> dumb to try and pull his arm free, and he was racing to think of
something.
> He saw a leg of Luna's moving to swipe at his face.  He followed it for a
